➜从送信使变成爽约代言人，这个古代高端智能生物，究竟经历了什么
http://www.sohu.com/a/419792580_624188	10549
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200921/032ff2dbf5b54008a030f9f410ce903a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在原来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人们提到鸽子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想到的会是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>Love &amp; Peace</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200921/f75e82822bef4098b409a2898fb9d28d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>美 味</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200921/f84fca85779b43fdbc7ef7754c5a1e0d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
