</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>电视剧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200921/64eb7aa82f1141adb20bb3e53e7eae44.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以及</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>亲子出游</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（<strong>不知道干嘛好不如喂喂鸽子吧</strong>）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>的趣味性担当</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200921/1410addcfde04915aa7c4160c081dbcf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而如今</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人们提到鸽子的次数</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是越来越多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但含义却只剩下一个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>爽·约</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200921/2c277ac4335e47c1bc0a0edf811899d9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">短短几年间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸽子竟从和平大使</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">变成了<strong>爽约代言人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这究竟是鸽了什么不得了的东西</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>才落得如今这番田地</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200921/6f3f199d69b94707b3761d3ab6af6c1a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那就得从</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸽子在电视剧里出镜率最高的技能</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飞鸽传书</strong>说起了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200921/cdfc58abff8c40e2b9f8eee1228fba51.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200921/73cb050c9ba2409eb28ed6fc9b7f50f0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">提起古代送信方式</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飞鸽传书</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一定是你最想尝试的一种</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟从小看电视剧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">剧里那些人送信都是——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不知道从哪掏出只鸽子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">往鸽腿上缠个<strong>小纸条or小竹筒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后跟鸽子来几句<strong>悄悄话</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸽子就<strong>秒懂</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自己该去哪儿该做什么了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">显得非常的<strong>高端智能</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200921/5b913f0a7cb648b0bb540307b9bf8aec.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">电视剧里鸽子把人鸽了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">顶多只有被人射下来吃了这个理由</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而现实就很骨感了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>鸽子可以从各个方面鸽你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人们之所以选择鸽子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当做<strong>智能送信机</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">主要是看中了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸽子一项独特的技能</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>归巢性</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">简称“恋家癖”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200921/23c8f1aa35794250adce99a7b8afcc9d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想拥有一批<strong>智能送信机</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你得做如下操作</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>首先</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在A地和B地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从<strong>鸽子蛋</strong>开始</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">分别饲养一批鸽子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让它们<strong>打小熟悉家的味道</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">知道在这儿<strong>稳定有吃的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>然后</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>交换地点——</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">A地的去B地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">B地的去A地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">互相试飞个几次</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">选出其中优秀的<strong>恋家癖</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">作为<strong>信鸽</strong>带上真正的战场</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>最后</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在突发军情的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就可以掏出一只信鸽绑上信息放飞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>靠着鸽子的恋家癖特性</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>AB两地就可以互相传递信息</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200921/6c431b29965544dabf52e8246810b94d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200921/035d4986303c44bbb3597f43f2076761.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你也看出来了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这操作<strong>非常坑</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为每只鸽子都是张——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200921/fd4da8f43a2846d38a83d8ae06e1e513.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">回到A地的鸽子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>并不会自觉的再回到B地</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">回到B地的也是同理</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以真就<strong>用一次少一只</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而在如此艰难的情况下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这张单程票</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有很大的几率<strong>坠机</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200921/5e2b54bd424c42cbac2e3afff1c7f61d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">1.<strong>天敌</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">除了鹰这样的<strong>食肉飞禽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>会射箭的人类</strong>也在地上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等着鸽子的路过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2.<strong>天气</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">恶劣天气将影响飞行速度</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至让它<strong>迷路</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">3.<strong>天注定</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万一休息途中<strong>遇见真爱</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万一休息途中<strong>被鸽带偏</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这信何年何月才能送到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那只有那只鸽子才知道了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200921/a29431d5791840cfbc813474be0e80e9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以使用飞鸽传书</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你可能遇见的真实情况是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200921/0fb4cce83a6a4edd8f368fce1e83955b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有人可能觉得</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这是因为送信距离太远导致</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那朕就拿现代的来说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">国庆节这些大型节日</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都有<strong>放鸽子</strong>这个保留节目</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟鸽子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也是象征<strong>爱与和平</strong>的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200921/ef9b6f6879b748db81092a080bb27706.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而就在北京市内征集的鸽子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从天安门放飞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">离归巢距离那么近</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也有<strong>10%</strong>左右的鸽子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>迷迷煳煳跟别的鸽子回家去了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">靠一己之力将放鸽子费从15万元</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">提高到了30万元</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200921/c0faac4b38fb406398487eb17efc4d93.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200921/bc950f7335cc4134a6469654aad9c896.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把鸽子当智能送信机后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人们发现鸽子回家顺序不定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你也知道的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一旦有了<strong>先后</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人类不自觉就开始<strong>瞎较劲</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200921/5b2030f1ae4b4669b3a2df7bd0790782.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人们开始拿鸽子来找乐子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">便有了新的游戏：<strong>赛鸽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">到了清朝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>赌鸽</strong>也出现了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们将参赛的鸽子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">按照<strong>《千字文》</strong>的顺序来<strong>编号标记好</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">放飞前参与赌博的人选择</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要哪个编号</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看最终赢得的鸽子的编号</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来<strong>瓜分大奖</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200921/61e44468743c46af8321ddea5071bb8f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">后期</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">玩法变得更加<strong>“彩票”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人们将《千字文》的前80个字</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">印在票上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">参与的人在上面圈10个字</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后由开奖处</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将80个字分别揉成小纸团</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">交给一只大白鸽子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">挑出20个当做<strong>中奖字码</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200921/3b1d659e68b24c97a9f406ebfff0a58e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只要在你提前圈出的字中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有<strong>5</strong>个字在鸽子挑出的中奖字码里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那恭喜你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">达到了<strong>中奖线</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这么看起来中奖率似乎不低</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟都没啥颜色、顺序的要求</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200921/035d4986303c44bbb3597f43f2076761.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你忘了挑纸团的鸽子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它是可以<strong>被训练的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开奖处是可以先挑出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大家选得最少的字</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后在纸团上<strong>做手脚</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">提前训练鸽子挑那类纸团</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为钱总是<strong>有去无回</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以放白鸽</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也成了一种爽约的说法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200921/7ed82d5a0b0f4064a3d142ed5b029df2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">买彩票至今未中奖的你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心里是不是平衡点了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟从古至今</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不管是鸽子选的还是电脑选的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你的钱都很公平的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>有 去 无 回</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200921/4d7b7632374d481db8ab397f584f638f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200921/fa078f6cffd44efd93662de74b0bd2f0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说出来你可能不信</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但放鸽子=爽约</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实有个很科学的解释</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸽子真的有拖延症</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">科学家做了实验</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">给鸽子两种选择</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">□ 简单但需要立刻做的任务</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">□ 难但可以拖延的任务</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">结果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸽子们都不约而同的选了那个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>难</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>但可以拖延的任务</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200921/bb66a12d534b484e887a035aab13ed34.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200921/6c431b29965544dabf52e8246810b94d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最绝的在于</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在人类的大脑机制下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要做的事儿其实都刻脑子里了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽然你在快乐摸鱼疯狂拖延</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可内心其实知道<strong>这逃不了的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在双重矛盾下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">导致人类在拖延的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">既快乐又焦虑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200921/adba100c42df47fd9049c216ebb370ca.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而鸽子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">脑子就<strong>花生米</strong>那么大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自然就没人类同款的拖延机制</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来约束它们的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以拖延这事儿对于它们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">压根就没心理负担</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更不用纠结</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>它们的拖</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>向来都是问心无愧的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200921/870d919df5a044efb12c7a078f1d4a77.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你们懂了吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">放鸽子这事儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是真的没办法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟鸽子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也控制不了自己</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200921/3c913f8b75044eff95e9f9697c1fdf7e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>